In connection with the outbreak of COVID: This is a crowdsourced tool that allows users to self-report symptoms and exposure history. This data could help in mapping teh spread of COVID-19 in the Philippines. With limited access to testing and testing capabilities, a large majority could not be tested. There could be a large gap in the data we have of people who are at risk in connection with the outbreak.
